import React from 'react';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';



function DailyTaskForm(props) {
    return (
        <Box className='section'>
            <Box className='container task-form'>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid item md={5} >
                        <input type="text" name='task_name' placeholder='Task Name' />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item md={5}>
                        <select name="category">
                            <option value="">Select Cotegory</option>
                            <option value="Nap Bug Task">Bug Task</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">Dev</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">staging</option>
                        </select>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item md={2}>
                        <input type="text" name='jira_id' placeholder='Jira ID' />
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid item md={3} >
                        <select name="Assignee">
                            <option value="">Select Assignee</option>
                            <option value="Nap Bug Task">Rohan</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">Kriti</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">Archana</option>
                        </select>                    
                        </Grid>
                    <Grid item md={3}>
                        <select name="Status">
                            <option value="">Select Status</option>
                            <option value="Nap Bug Task">Completed</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">Pending</option>
                            <option value="Nap Dev">Processing</option>
                        </select>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item md={3}>
                        <input type="date" name='due_date' />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item md={3}>
                        <input type="date" name='go_live' />
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default DailyTaskForm;
